svg.title: Berlin's district Information
svg.desc: An interactive map depicting the basic information of the districts situated in Berlin

defs.script:
<!--*********************************************************************** -->
<!-- VARIABLES, ARRAY with all used data -->
				

var infoBoard = [];
	infoBoard[0] = ["State", "Area (km²)", "Unemployment", "Population", "schools", "Restaurant", "Schools", "Restaurant", "Sport-Hall", "Parking-alot", "Shopping Mall", "Population Berlin"];
	infoBoard[1] = ["Mitte", 39.47, "337,593", 892, "3,422", "73.3", 13.4, 7.1, 6.2];
	infoBoard[2] = ["Friedrichshain-Kreuzberg", 200, "263,526", 892, "3,422", 77.1, 9.8, 6.8,6.3,26.3];
	infoBoard[3] = ["Pankow", 103.01, "371,438", 892, "3,422", 70.5, 15.2, 7.5, 6.8];
	infoBoard[4] = ["Charlottenburg-Wilmersdorf", 64.72, "302,313", 892, "3,422", 66.3, 22.7, 6.4, 4.7];
	infoBoard[5] = ["Spandau", 91.91, "222,300", 892, "3,422", 64.1, 22.5, 8.0, 5.5];
	infoBoard[6] = ["Steglitz-Zehlendorf", 25.4, "284,313", 892, "3,422", 61.8, 25.4, 7.8, 5];
	infoBoard[7] = ["Tempelhof-Schöneberg",53.09, "324,208", 892, "3,422", 67.1, 20.6, 7.2, 5.1];
	infoBoard[8] = ["Neukölln",44.93, "311,943", 892, "3,422", 69.1, 17.3, 7.7, 6.0];
	infoBoard[9] = ["Treptow-Köpenick",168.42, "244,016", 892, "3,422", 64,23.8, 7.4, 5.5];
	infoBoard[10] = ["Marzahn-Hellersdorf",61.74, "251,007", 892, "3,422", 69.5, 17.1, 7.4, 6.1];
	infoBoard[11] = ["Lichtenberg",52.29, "262,760", 892, "3,422", 67.5,20.2, 6.4, 5.9];
	infoBoard[12] = ["Reinickendorf",89.46, "246,412", 892, "3,422", 62.7, 23.9, 8, 5.4];
	infoBoard[13] = ["Berlin",89.46,3422,3422 ,3422,3422,3422,3422, 50,1,1, "3422"];

		
<!--*********************************************************************** -->
<!-- INFO BOX VALUE DISPLAY -->	

		function dispData(evt){
	      	var srcID = evt.target.getAttributeNS(null,'id').substr(8);
	      	document.getElementById('Name').firstChild.data = infoBoard[srcID][0];
			document.getElementById('area').firstChild.data = infoBoard[srcID][1];
			document.getElementById('Unemp').firstChild.data = infoBoard[srcID][2];
			document.getElementById('Popul').firstChild.data = infoBoard[srcID][3];
			document.getElementById('schools').firstChild.data = infoBoard[srcID][4];
		}
			
		function barGraph(evt){
			var srcID = evt.target.getAttributeNS(null,'id').substr(8);
			//schools
			var anchor = document.getElementById("h_1");
			var att = document.createAttribute("width");
			att.value = infoBoard[srcID][4];//10
			anchor.setAttributeNode(att);
			//Restaurant
			var anchor = document.getElementById("h_2");
			var att = document.createAttribute("width");
			att.value = infoBoard[srcID][5];
			anchor.setAttributeNode(att);
			//Sport-Hall
			var anchor = document.getElementById("h_3");
			var att = document.createAttribute("width");
			att.value = infoBoard[srcID][6];
			anchor.setAttributeNode(att);
			//Parking-alot
			var anchor = document.getElementById("h_4");
			var att = document.createAttribute("width");
			att.value = infoBoard[srcID][7];
			anchor.setAttributeNode(att);
			//Shopping Mall
			var anchor = document.getElementById("h_5");
			var att = document.createAttribute("width");
			att.value = infoBoard[srcID][8];
			anchor.setAttributeNode(att);
		}
			
<!--*********************************************************************** -->
